# 通知服務層模式

## 標準結構

每個通知平台需要兩個檔案：

```
Services/
├── I{Platform}Service.cs   # 介面
└── {Platform}Service.cs    # 實作
```

## 介面定義

```csharp
namespace WebhookForTG.Services;

public interface I{Platform}Service
{
    Task<(bool Success, string? Error)> SendMessageAsync(string message);
}
```

## 實作範本

```csharp
public class {Platform}Service : I{Platform}Service
{
    private readonly HttpClient _httpClient;
    private readonly string _token;       // 從 appsettings 取得
    private readonly ILogger<{Platform}Service> _logger;

    public {Platform}Service(HttpClient httpClient, IConfiguration configuration, ILogger<{Platform}Service> logger)
    {
        _httpClient = httpClient;
        _token = configuration["{Section}:{Key}"]
            ?? throw new InvalidOperationException("{Section}:{Key} is not configured.");
        _logger = logger;
    }

    public async Task<(bool Success, string? Error)> SendMessageAsync(string message)
    {
        try
        {
            // 呼叫平台 API...
            _logger.LogInformation("{Platform} 發送成功");
            return (true, null);
        }
        catch (Exception ex)
        {
            _logger.LogError(ex, "{Platform} 發送時發生例外");
            return (false, ex.Message);
        }
    }
}
```

## Program.cs 注冊方式

```csharp
builder.Services.AddHttpClient<I{Platform}Service, {Platform}Service>();
```

## 規則
- 服務層不可拋例外給上層，一律用 tuple 回傳
- 失敗時記錄 `LogWarning` 或 `LogError`，成功記錄 `LogInformation`
- 每個平台各自獨立的 `HttpClient`（透過 `AddHttpClient` 注冊）
